snippet.title: Leap Year: March Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3458170/Leap_Year_March/
Itch: https://managore.itch.io/leap-year-march

Leap Year: March continues the adventure for players who have beaten Leap Year and want an even greater challenge. Use the same tools you learned in Leap Year to explore another hand drawn world that’s both larger and much more complex. Master your understanding of Leap Year’s secrets to complete another month of your calendar.

Leap Year: March is DLC for Leap Year
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2951770/Leap_Year/
Itch: https://managore.itch.io/leap-year
